summary: Marvel Dismisses Georgia Crew Members as 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3' Goes on Hold
title: Marvel Dismisses Georgia Crew Members as 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3' Goes on Hold
body:
Marvel Dismisses Georgia Crew Members as ‘Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3’ Goes on Hold

Marvel’s return to Atlanta is suffering from a rough start, with the production of Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3 reportedly put on hold.

According to reports, Marvel dismissed crew members for the sequel and producers have stopped preproduction for “regrouping.”

The Hollywood Reporter reports the project was scheduled for preproduction this fall but production has been stopped following the…
